sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Client
    participant EC as EventController
    participant EB as EventBob
    participant HA as HttpEventHandlerAdapter
    participant RM as Remote Microlith
    participant RH as Remote EventHandler

    C->>EC: POST /events (EventDto JSON)
    EC->>EB: handle(Event)
    EB->>HA: handle(Event)
    Note over HA: Convert Event → EventDto
    HA->>RM: HTTP POST /events (EventDto JSON)
    RM->>RH: handle(Event)
    RH-->>RM: Event (response)
    Note over RM: Convert Event → EventDto
    RM-->>HA: EventDto JSON
    Note over HA: Convert EventDto → Event
    HA-->>EB: Event
    EB-->>EC: Event
    Note over EC: Convert Event → EventDto
    EC-->>C: EventDto JSON
